                  ) : (
                    <>
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" className="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M8 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-1M8 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M8 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 0h2a2 2 0 012 2v3m2 4H10m0 0l3-3m-3 3l3 3" />
                      </svg>
                      統一複製所有清單規格
                    </>
                  )}
                </button>
                <p className="mt-3 text-center text-slate-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
                  點擊將一鍵複製該型號下所有零件規格內容，方便貼入下單系統
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ) : (
          <div className="text-center py-40 bg-slate-950/20 border-2 border-dashed border-slate-800 rounded-[3rem]">
            <div className="inline-block p-8 bg-slate-900 rounded-full mb-6 border border-slate-800 shadow-inner">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" className="h-16 w-16 text-indigo-500 opacity-40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={1} d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
